## Input Formats

| Format | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `xes` | IEEE XES event log |
| `ocel2` | OCEL 2.0 object-centric event log (JSON) |
| `handle` | Pre-loaded in-process WASM handle (use `load_ocel` or `discover_dfg` first) |
| `none` | No input required |

